data.allRelevantTextIncludingURLs: For details on upcoming live music events, visit [Monqui Presents](https://monqui.com) and follow them on social media platforms like [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/monqui_presents/) and [TikTok](https://www.tiktok.com/@monqui_presents). You can find specific venues such as [Oregon](https://monqui.com/venues/oregon/), [Washington](https://monqui.com/washington-canada), and [McMenamins Edgefield](https://monqui.com/venue/mcmenamins-edgefield/) for upcoming shows.
